data.description: Welcome to this spacious single-family home in the highly sought-after community of Caravel Farms. Boasting 4 bedrooms and 2 1/2 baths, this residence offers the perfect combination of comfort and privacy. Situated on a quiet cul-de-sac and surrounded by a wooded area, this home creates an enchanting retreat-like ambiance.  As you step inside, you will enter into the foyer and leads to sunlit living spaces that seamlessly flow together.  Main level offers separate living room, dining room, kitchen and inviting family room complete with wood burning fireplace.  Off the family room is access to the 2 car garage, laundry area and half bath.  The upstairs main suite is a true sanctuary, offering a generous layout, a walk-in closet, and an en-suite bathroom. Three additional well-appointed bedrooms provide plenty of space for family or guests to relax and unwind.  Step outside into your private oasis, where a sparkling pool awaits.   Don't miss your opportunity to own this remarkable property.
